Pseudolight v0.0.1

Usage: pseudolight <args>

Args:
    --debug:            Enable debug logging
    --install-daemon    Installs and runs pseudolight as a daemon
    --uninstall-daemon  Uninstalls the pseudolight daemon if it is installed
    --edit-config       Opens pseudolight.conf in your text editor
    --erase-config      Deletes pseudolight's configuration from the system
    --purge             Completely removes pseudolight from the system (configs, daemons)

Info:
    config is stored in ~/.config/pseudolight/pseudolight.conf by default